The paper discusses consensus dynamics in a decentralised multiagent system, specifically in the context of the kilobot robotic platform. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Multiagent Systems (cs.MA), Robotics (cs.RO), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of theoretical models and empirical validation, which are common themes in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.MA, cs.RO, and cs.SY, followed by cs.AI and cs.NE.
